    <name>
      <text>Calculating Monthly Installments on a Hire Purchase Agreement</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="moodle_auto_format">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>An item costs Ksh.\({@cash_price@}\).
A deposit of \({@deposit_rate@}\).% is required, and the balance is to be paid over 24 months.
Interest is charged a \({@interest_rate@}\)% on the balance.</p><p>
Calculate:</p><p>
a) The deposit amount</p><p>
</p><p>[[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]][[feedback:prt1]]</p>
b) The total amount to be paid in installments</p><p>
</p><p>[[input:ans2]] [[validation:ans2]][[feedback:prt2]]</p>
c) The monthly installment amount
</p><p>[[input:ans3]] [[validation:ans3]][[feedback:prt3]]</p>]]></text>
    </questiontext>
